      "content": "but that's the thing... it's not even about being \"disposable.\" it's just that the silence sounds so much better than the noise of trying to matter. if i just stopped existing, everything would just go back to being perfectly calm. no one would be hurt, no one would have to deal with me, and the world would just keep spinning like nothing ever happened. it seems almost... peaceful. doesn't it?",
